        <description>THE NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE HAS ISSUED SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WATCH
575 IN EFFECT UNTIL 11 PM MDT THIS EVENING FOR THE FOLLOWING
AREAS

IN MONTANA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 8 COUNTIES

IN NORTHEAST MONTANA

DAWSON                GARFIELD              MCCONE
PETROLEUM             PRAIRIE               RICHLAND
ROOSEVELT             WIBAUX

THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF CIRCLE, CULBERTSON, FAIRVIEW,
GLENDIVE, JORDAN, POPLAR, RICHEY, SIDNEY, TERRY, WIBAUX, WINNETT,
AND WOLF POINT.
</description>
